{"tid":498346,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔人道】愛護動物協會：釘帶對狗隻會造成極大傷害","createTime":"2017-12-13T16:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T17:49:08.000Z","uid":10958,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3dfaf89a8209b6637fbde0f85a8e6e582d37f89f","tid":498346,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"<strong>【唔人道】愛護動物協會：釘帶對狗隻會造成極大傷害</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.next.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/12/3503380/20171212_ment_fred03_ping_m.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.next.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F3503380%2F20171212_ment_fred03_ping_m.mp4&d=nxZBT4WBp6x4OVjBS4GNsk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=b0e0310e\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.next.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/12/3503380/20171212_ment_fred03_ping_m.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭俊弘於是幫Riley戴上一條有鋒利倒鈎鐵鏈狗帶，唔理隻狗會因此被整傷，諗住可以控制隻狗，但愛護動物協會侯安娜醫生強烈反對狗主使用釘帶，她表示在任何情況下都不應該使用倒鈎頸圈，對動物帶來不必要的傷害，於香港使用此類頸圈可能會觸犯法例甚至變成虐畜；對於狗隻訓練方法應該以獎勵及肯定方法，而不是承受痛楚，倒鈎頸圈除為狗隻帶來皮肉上的痛苦，心理上亦有嚴重的創傷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20171212/large/1513091226_bcde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20171212%2Flarge%2F1513091226_bcde.jpg&h=cfe117cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而保護遺棄動物協會創辦人陳淑娟表示，一般的狗種都不需要用到倒鈎頸圈，以往訓練員只會用於特別唔聽話、難控制及厚毛的犬種上；陳小姐更表示狗圈的用途是為狗隻帶來服從的信息，一旦運用不當會對狗隻造成極大傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20171213/563409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20171213%2F563409&d=nxZBT4WBp6x4OVjBS4GNsk4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=eb7a0d2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20171213%2F563409&h=124fa630\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20171213/563409</a>"},{"pid":"cdb1e116c3c92fd92aa9d01f51934eb13ed445f8","tid":498346,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"459d0907efb572794bf4b8c0d52d094901abde66","tid":498346,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}